                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/slider-3.jpg" alt="Slider Image 3" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption slider-msg" role="option">
                <p>
                    Watch Your Favourite TV Shows<br />
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/slider-4.jpg" alt="Slider Image 4" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption slider-msg" role="option">
                <p>
                    Recharge your Package Online<br />
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="#">
